---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<section id="faq">
    <h3>FAQ</h3>
    <div class="faq">
        <details>
            <summary>Will Liveboot modify my disks?</summary>
            <p>
                No. It will run entirely in RAM by default. Tools that write to
                disks ask for confirmation and are opt-in.
            </p>
        </details>
        <details>
            <summary>What hardware is supported?</summary>
            <p>
                Anything a standard Linux kernel supports. We target modern
                x86-64 and common Wi-Fi/Ethernet chipsets. ARM and RISC-V builds
                may follow.
            </p>
        </details>
        <details>
            <summary>How big is the image and how fast does it boot?</summary>
            <p>
                We aim for a small footprint with fast, network-enabled boots.
                Exact sizes depend on enabled toolsets per release.
            </p>
        </details>
        <details>
            <summary>Can I customize the toolset?</summary>
            <p>
                With a bit of fiddling, yes. The NixOS base allows you to build
                custom variants or enable extra modules.
            </p>
        </details>
        <details>
            <summary>Is Secure Boot supported?</summary>
            <p>
                Planned. We're working on signed artifacts and reproducible
                builds; roadmap will note progress.
            </p>
        </details>
        <details>
            <summary>Is this website AI generated?</summary>
            <p>
                Yes, for now. We just wanted to quickly get something up and running.
            </p>
        </details>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .faq {
        max-width: var(--maxw);
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    details {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-stroke);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    summary {
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    details[open] {
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
    }

    details p {
        color: var(--muted);
        margin: 8px 0 0;
    }
</style>
